  "title": "自制卡片的间隔可以排得更长",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"Mwr-vJc6\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Andy_Matuschak\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Andy Matuschak</a> 针对《量子国度》也发表过类似观点：如果你遇到的卡片，来自于你正在阅读的文章，那么你对卡片测试的事实有足够的了解，因此相比于外语词汇卡片，这张卡片的复习间隔可以拉得更长。你充分理解材料，并用材料制作卡片，这些卡片也同样适用。</p><h3>另见</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"QDD_5umj\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Anki_deck_options\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Anki 牌组设置</a> ——内有关于排期的更多思考</li></ul><h3>链接到本文</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"SvcaV5Jr\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Anki_deck_options\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Anki 牌组设置</a> (<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DSpecial%3AWhatLinksHere%26target%3DAnki%2Bdeck%2Boptions\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">← links</a>)</li></ul><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"ciMnci-N\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a>汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 Shom、校对 <span class=\"nolink\">Albert</span><br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Cards_created_by_oneself_can_be_scheduled_more_aggressively\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Cards created by oneself can be scheduled more aggressively</a></blockquote>",
